overview: Americans move to a foreign country all in the name of love. Will uprooting their lives in the United States pay off, or will they be packing up and moving back to America brokenhearted?

seasons.name: Season 1
seasons.overview: How far would you go for love? Fans of 90 Day Fiance have seen lovestruck foreigners make the big adjustment of moving to America, and now theyll get to follow hopeful couples where its the American moving abroad.

episodes.name: All in the Name of Love
episodes.overview: Four Americans who have found love abroad brace to leave home permanently. Corey must follow his love to Ecuador. Single mom Tiffany takes her son to South Africa. Grandmother Jenny prepares to be with her soulmate in India, and Paul is Brazil-bound.

episodes.name: Embargos and Ultimatums
episodes.overview: Evelin gives Corey a life-changing ultimatum. Tiffany comes clean to her family about Ronald's dark past. Paul learns that he can't bring Karine to the States. Jenny's friends think moving to India is the worst decision of her life.

episodes.name: It's Go Time
episodes.overview: Corey breaks the news to his parents that he's moving to Ecuador. Laura is leaving her son behind to move to Qatar. Karine is disappointed in Paul. Sumit faces his parents as Jenny flies to India.

episodes.name: Big Expectations
episodes.overview: Jenny arrives in India but does Sumit have cold feet? Paul finally arrives in Brazil and surprises Karine. Laura drops a bomb on her brother, revealing some big news.  And Tiffany is off to South Africa hoping she's made the right decision for her son.

episodes.name: No Looking Back
episodes.overview: Corey begins to second guess his life-changing move to Ecuador. Sumit wants to transform Jenny into a traditional Indian woman. Tiffany and Daniel pick up Ronald from rehab. Jihoon hopes he can get his parents to change their mind about Deavan.

episodes.name: Another World
episodes.overview: Corey's arrival in Ecuador is not as he expected.  Deavan is off to a rocky start with Jihoon's parents.  Laura takes drastic measures to improve her sex life with Aladin.  Paul receives upsetting news regarding his permanent residency in Brazil.

episodes.name: Broken Promises
episodes.overview: Ronald puts Tiffany's trust to the test. Sumit has been keeping a secret from Jenny. Facing deportation, Paul seeks legal advice. Laura has second thoughts about leaving her son behind. Deavan fails to impress Jihoon's parents.

episodes.name: Chickening Out
episodes.overview: Laura finally arrives in Qatar. Tiffany confronts Ronald about his bachelor party. Deavan takes Jihoon's parents out on the town. Corey attempts to win over Evelin's family with some magic tricks. Jenny and Sumit receive crushing news.

episodes.name: Ripped Apart
episodes.overview: As the wedding approaches, Tiffany's son Daniel expresses doubts about South Africa. Sumit is summoned home by his parents. Paul and Karine embark on a daunting journey up the Amazon. Jihoon's proposal backfires, and Evelin is over Corey's attitude.

episodes.name: Rolling the Dice
episodes.overview: Ronald has to confront his demons. Laura's new sex toy offends Aladin. Corey and Evelin have a very different vision for their future. Paul faces Karine's parents with upsetting news. Sumit leaves Jenny to go home to his parents.

episodes.name: Blind Trust
episodes.overview: Ron's sobriety distracts Tiffany on her big day; Deavan breaks some unfortunate news to Jihoon; Laura sees another side of Aladin; Paul discovers that Karine is talking to another man; Corey faces his past with Evelin.

episodes.name: Baby, Come Back
episodes.overview: Jenny goes out at night without Sumit; Deavan doubts Jihoon is responsible enough to support their family; Tiffany and Ronald go apartment shopping and worry about safety; Karine is concerned that Paul can't financially take care of her and the baby.

episodes.name: Breaking Point
episodes.overview: After Sumit returns home to Jenny they get a huge surprise; Karine reaches her breaking point; Corey discovers even more about Evelin's past; Deavan questions if Jihoon can support their family; Laura feels homesick in Qatar.

episodes.name: The Great Unknown
episodes.overview: Tiffany and Ronald surprise everyone with big news; Laura pleads with her son to come to her wedding; Deavan leaves for South Korea, but worries Jihoon isn't prepared; Corey asks Evelin to cut off her ex; Karine and her mom leave Paul behind.

episodes.name: Walking A Tight Rope
episodes.overview: Deavan's arrival in South Korea does not go as she expected; Ronald's gambling addiction causes issues with Tiffany; Paul tries to get back in Karine's good graces; Jenny's daughter confronts Sumit.

episodes.name: Fool's Gold
episodes.overview: Jihoon reveals a huge secret about his past to Deavan; Jenny and Sumit's relationship reaches a boiling point; Paul and Karine become parents; tensions build when Laura's son arrives in Tunisia and meets Aladin.

episodes.name: Shattered Dreams
episodes.overview: Jenny hears shocking news about Sumit; Laura is torn between Liam and Aladin; Corey returns to Evelin in Ecuador; Paul's mother arrives in Brazil; Tiffany worries about giving birth in South Africa.

episodes.name: Torn
episodes.overview: Sumit reveals his truth; Deavan discovers more troubling information about Jihoon's past; Corey returns to Ecuador with less than a month on his visa to convince Evelin to wed; Liam gives Aladin an ultimatum.

episodes.name: Falling Apart
episodes.overview: Jenny and Sumit face each other for the first time since she found out he is married; the issues between Laura, her son and Aladin come to a head; Paul's mother gives him a wake-up call; Tiffany makes a difficult decision for her family

episodes.name: Never Let Me Go
episodes.overview: A distraught Jenny no longer feels at home in India; Deavan struggles during her traditional Korean wedding ceremony; Evelin must decide if she wants to marry Corey; Tiffany worries about Ronald's recovery when she and Daniel leave.

episodes.name: Tell All: Part 1
episodes.overview: The cast take a deep dive into the details of their most intense moments the season along with unleashing some surprising updates.

episodes.name: Tell All: Part 2
episodes.overview: Shaun Robinson dives back in with the couples and continues to uncover surprising updates on about their relationships.

episodes.overview: Shekinah meets up with Sarper's ex to learn the truth. Corona gets an icy welcome from Ingi. Lily takes Josh for a traditional ear massage. Tatha's parents pressure her about giving them grandchildren.

episodes.name: One Fine Bidet
episodes.overview: Shekinah confronts Sarper about his ex. The three promises James made to Meitalia's parents come back to haunt him. Josh's jealousy issues frustrate Lily. Statler and Dempsey's reunion is overshadowed by Statler's anxiety.

episodes.name: A Risky Business
episodes.overview: Chaos ensues after James and Tatha tell her family they're staying in Indonesia. Joanne and Sean plan how to reveal they've been married for 2 years. Corona tells Ingi she's been hiding her anger from him. Statler is stunned by the look of the campervan.

episodes.name: Much Ado About Everything
episodes.overview: Joanne reveals the truth to her mom before leaving for Ireland. James and Tatha end up in tears when things get lost in translation. Lily's sister presses Josh on his lack of income. Statler and Dempsey face a frigid first night in their van.

episodes.name: Some Kind Of Awful
episodes.overview: Corona has a surprising first encounter with Ingi's parents. Joanne and her sons leave for Ireland to meet Sean. Statler and Dempsey hit the open road. An argument between Sarper and Shekinah ruins their birthday.

episodes.name: (Dis)Enchanted
episodes.overview: Corona's family grills Ingi on his intentions. Statler is shocked to find out Dempsey has money put away, while she's in debt. Lily asks Josh if he wants to end their marriage. Sarper reflects on his actions as Shekinah opens up about her past.

episodes.name: Eat, Play, Lie
episodes.overview: Dempsey reaches a breaking point while Statler battles a panic attack at sea. Shekinah gives Sarper a stern ultimatum. James makes a heartbreaking admission to Tatha. Sean bonds with Joanne's sons but feels the pressure of keeping secrets.

episodes.name: No Hard Feelings?
episodes.overview: Joanne and Sean finally come clean about their marriage. Shekinah and Sarper turn to a therapist for help. As Statler's panic attack continues, Dempsey is ready to call it quits. Josh's lack of intimacy leaves Lily feeling unloved.

episodes.name: There's Something About JoJo
episodes.overview: Joanne's kids are stunned when they learn more about her hope for the future. Corona's dream of becoming a midwife is in jeopardy. Meitalia gives James a timeline for having children. Josh surprises Lily with a romantic gesture.

episodes.name: Reality Frights
episodes.overview: Shekinah moves back in with Sarper and uncovers a lie. Corona is on a deadline to make a decision about her future. Statler and Dempsey attempt to rebuild their relationship. Josh and Lily clash in front of Josh's brother.

episodes.name: Fools Rushed In
episodes.overview: James tells Meitalia they are running out of money. Shekinah goes under the knife. Josh's brother tries to help him and Lily see eye to eye. Joanne's son pokes holes in her plan to move to Ireland.

episodes.name: Daughter Of The Bride
episodes.overview: Lily's daughter puts Josh in the hot seat. Statler hits a roadblock on her first day back to work. Meitalia makes James tell her parents that he doesn't want kids. Sarper is tested during Shekinah's post-op recovery.

episodes.name: Donna Mia
episodes.overview: Corona learns Ingi's true feelings about marriage. Sean and Joanne's mom Donna finally meet, and she has questions. James fears Tatha's sister will drive a wedge between them. Lily's daughter Vivian worries about her mom's lack of a sex life.

episodes.name: Bride and Prejudice
episodes.overview: Josh urges Lily to move forward with their wedding ceremony, so she sets a test for him. Attempts to make up after their first fight go awry for Corona and Ingi. James and Tatha's elaborate, traditional Indonesian wedding is full of surprises.

episodes.name: (500) Days of Bummer
episodes.overview: James insists they need to return to the United States, and the realization that Tatha must choose between her husband and her family hits back hard. Sarper hatches a plan to keep Shekinah in Turkey. Statler and Dempsey reach the ultimate crossroads in their relationship.

episodes.name: He's Just Not That into U.S.
episodes.overview: Corona is torn between her dream job and her dream man. Lily has doubts about her future with Josh. Joanne and Sean are back to square one. Shekinah is thrilled by the traditional Turkish engagement ceremony.

episodes.name: Tell All Part 1
episodes.overview: The cast of The Other Way sits down with Shaun Robinson in NYC, with more couples together in person than ever before. A friend from Sarper's past joins the stage, everyone debates Josh and Lily's sex life, and one couple reveals a shocking break up.
